FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://localhost:3000/api/v2

# Library API

API for managing library resources including Books, Members, and Loans.

---

# Group Books

## Books Collection [/books]

### List All Books [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[Book])

---

### Create a New Book [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (BookInput)

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Book)

+ Response 400 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Error)

---

## Book Details [/books/{id}]

+ Parameters
    + id: `book-123` (string, required) - The unique identifier of the book.

---

### Get Book Details [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Book)

+ Response 404 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Error)

---

### Delete a Book [DELETE]

+ Response 204

+ Response 404 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Error)

---

# Group Members

## Members Collection [/members]

### List All Members [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[Member])

---

### Create a Member [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (Member)

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Member)

+ Response 400 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Error)

---

# Group Loans

## Loans Collection [/loans]

### Create a Loan [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (Loan)

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Loan)

+ Response 400 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Error)

---

# Data Structures

## Book (object)
+ id: `book-123` (string)
+ title: `Node.js Programming` (string)
+ author: `John Doe` (string)

## BookInput (object)
+ title: `Node.js Programming` (string)
+ author: `John Doe` (string)

## Member (object)
+ id: `mem-456` (string)
+ name: `Alice Smith` (string)

## Loan (object)
+ id: `loan-789` (string)
+ bookId: `book-123` (string)
+ memberId: `mem-456` (string)

## Error (object)
+ message: `Resource not found` (string)